 i didnt rob them with a gun or a knife  i just made them a little deal  let me borrow two dollars today  i said  and ill bring you five dollars next week  the investment was too good to pass up  and  se razlikuje od stava saveta mladih  koji su takodje na strani predsednika branko ruzic i dejan backovic  svojevremeno najveci branioci i zastupnici lika i dela slobodana milosevica  danas su se
